==民主派總辭==
因應四名民主派議員被政府取消資格，其他民主派议员宣布集体辞职以抗議[[全國人大常委會|全國人大常委會]]的決定<ref>{{cite news |title=香港立法会：中国人大常委会决议打击民主派　四议员即时撤职　民主派集体辞任抗议 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-54884224 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2020-12-03 |archive-date=2020-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214094536/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-54884224 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，立法會在2020年11月12日表示，已收到其餘民主派的辭職信。<ref>{{Cite web|title=立法會秘書處：已收全部 15 名民主派辭職信　許智峯、毛孟靜今明生效　其餘下月生效|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95-%E5%B7%B2%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8-15-%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E4%BF%A1-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88-%E5%85%B6%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88/|accessdate=2020-11-11|work=立場報道|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221051322/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95-%E5%B7%B2%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8-15-%E5%90%8D%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E4%BF%A1-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%9F%E9%9D%9C%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88-%E5%85%B6%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=民主派議員分批交辭職信|url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559714-20201112.htm|accessdate=2020-11-12|work=香港電台|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107020216/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559714-20201112.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

